title: Focus Live At The Rainbow 1973 - Brazilian TV Broadcast.
description:
Firstly this is my first upload so apologies if there are any problems.

This is the full Brazilian TV broadcast of Focus\&#039; famous Rainbow Theatre concert at which the \"At The Rainbow\" album was recorded.

It contains all tracks on the album plus Jan Akkerman\&#039;s solo lute performance of a piece by John Dowland.

It is a RAR file in VCD format ready to burn straight to VCD.
Enjoy it-it is hard to find in good quality.

I promise you all-it is a 100% clean file.

:-)
